        <p>Buildertrend wins this comparison for the vast majority of remodeling contractors. It was built with residential workflows in mind, including the specific tools — selections, homeowner portal, draw billing, lead management — that define how remodeling businesses operate. Procore is powerful software built for a different market.</p>

        <p>Don't buy Procore because it sounds more professional. Buy the tool that fits your business model.</p>

